            There is a clear and obvious conflict of interest and it is not satisfactory to rely on the goodwill of local authorities. That may in many cases be there but we
            
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_147gc' title='Col. 147GC &mdash; HL Deb 30 January 2001 vol 621 c147GC' name='column_147gc' href='#column_147gc' rel='bookmark'>147GC</a>
