      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0621P0-03305'>
        <a name='S5LV0621P0_20010130_GCR_131'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-ralph-palmer' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0621P0_20010130_GCR_131' title='Link to this speech by Mr Ralph Palmer' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
