          <p class='first-para'>
            I have tried desperately not to be political in this debate. It is an issue that goes across all parties. However, after the debate yesterday and having asked my Question today, for the Minister to say that many children lack the capacity to make such
            
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_175gc' title='Col. 175GC &mdash; HL Deb 30 January 2001 vol 621 c175GC' name='column_175gc' href='#column_175gc' rel='bookmark'>175GC</a>
