      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0621P0-03417'>
        <a name='S5LV0621P0_20010130_GCR_243'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-emily-blatch' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0621P0_20010130_GCR_243' title='Link to this speech by Ms Emily Blatch' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-emily-blatch" title="Ms Emily Blatch">Baroness Blatch</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            I apologise to the noble Baroness. I was arguing against the specific amendments which called for the abolition of this part of the Bill.
          </p>
